      • Resistance

        public Resistance(String geneName,
                  String typeOfMutation,
                  String change,
                  String filter,
                  int genomePosition,
                  String drugName)
        Create an resistance annotation.
        Parameters:
        geneName - The name of the gene.
        typeOfMutation - The kind of mutation.
        change - The description of what happens exactly in the mutation.
        filter - The filter that was used to get the data.
        genomePosition - The position in the genome.
        drugName - The name of the drug for which the mutation causes resistance.
